This is Paris.

54
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:21,399
And we are here.

55
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:23,759
This little territory is Navarre.

56
00:05:23,840 --> 00:05:26,519
Your kingdom.

57
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:31,359
- And all of this is France?
- Yes, that's France.

58
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:40,639
- They're bringing in the harvest.
- You're not a peasant, Prince.

59
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:45,039
You are to be the King of France
if your mother has her way.

60
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:48,399
I don't want to go to Paris.

61
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:51,359
I want to stay here, with you.

62
00:05:51,440 --> 00:05:54,639
My boy. You shall have no choice.

63
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:56,439
Run along.

64
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:23,079
Take this sword, my Prince.

65
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:24,559
