131
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:25,879
Margot is a sow!

132
00:12:25,960 --> 00:12:28,159
One does not speak so of one's sister.

133
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:32,599
- You are the King!
- In the eyes of the world maybe.

134
00:12:32,680 --> 00:12:34,399
In truth...

135
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:36,519
Leave us.

136
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:43,119
Mind your words before my maids!

137
