144
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:09,679
If there's a threat to you, it's Guise!

145
00:13:09,760 --> 00:13:12,879
He pretends to be
even more Catholic than us.

146
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:15,159
The people love him.

147
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:20,839
I'll have him castrated, mother.

148
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:24,439
- I am the King.
- You are nothing.

149
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:27,079
Nothing at all, without me.

150
00:13:28,680 --> 00:13:29,719
Let me take care of it.

151
00:13:32,240 --> 00:13:35,159
What is my brother, the King,
saying about me?

152
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:38,239
- The truth.
- Why did you sleep with Guise?

153
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:41,319
You know he covets the throne!

154
00:13:41,400 --> 00:13:43,959
How dare you?

155
00:13:45,240 --> 00:13:48,159
With Guise!

156
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:50,279
You...

157
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:51,799
How dare you?

158
00:13:51,880 --> 00:13:55,319
- You whore!
- Put her over your knee.

159
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,919
You'll pay for that!

160
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:27,599
You'll pay.

161
00:14:27,680 --> 00:14:29,239
That's enough.

162
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:31,559
We shall marry you off.

163
00:14:33,040 --> 00:14:36,199
But certainly not to Guise!

164
00:14:36,280 --> 00:14:37,799
To Henry of Navarre.

165
00:14:39,840 --> 00:14:41,359
You can't be serious?

166
00:14:42,400 --> 00:14:44,639
We've never been more serious.

167
00:14:44,720 --> 00:14:46,999
You've lost your minds.

168
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:49,319
I want peace in my country.

169
