173
00:15:05,200 --> 00:15:07,319
Your marriage is a symbol.

174
00:15:07,400 --> 00:15:11,319
- The reconciliation of our faiths.
- Over my dead body!

175
00:15:28,880 --> 00:15:32,639
My son, you made a wise decision.

176
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:37,679
No farewell kiss?

177
00:15:37,760 --> 00:15:40,439
We shall negotiate skilfully.

178
00:15:40,520 --> 00:15:43,119
Catherine shall not have it all her way.

179
00:15:49,680 --> 00:15:53,479
Remember our maxim:
Conquer or die.

180
00:15:53,560 --> 00:15:55,319
Enough have died.

181
00:15:59,320 --> 00:16:01,519
Dear Catherine,
take care of our mother.

182
00:16:02,160 --> 00:16:03,239
Henry, I'm scared.

183
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:04,839
The Admiral will protect you.

184
00:16:07,680 --> 00:16:09,359
Go.

185
00:16:18,400 --> 00:16:20,439
What do you think, Beauvois?

186
