There are worse sacrifices than
sharing a bed with a beautiful woman.

187
00:16:30,480 --> 00:16:33,119
You know I love you like a son.

188
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:37,439
Nothing will make you happier than
the joy of those you bring peace to.

189
00:16:38,400 --> 00:16:41,079
For violence is strong

190
00:16:41,160 --> 00:16:43,039
but kindness is stronger.

191
00:16:54,240 --> 00:16:57,439
I hope you had a good journey.

192
00:16:57,880 --> 00:17:00,199
Paris is far away.

193
00:17:00,280 --> 00:17:03,799
And I am all the more grateful
that you came.

194
00:17:03,880 --> 00:17:06,039
Don't be too hasty.

195
00:17:06,680 --> 00:17:10,359
Dear friend,
we will come to an agreement.

196
00:17:11,240 --> 00:17:12,919
What is religion in the end?

197
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:16,319
Religion is the substance of my life!

198
00:17:18,160 --> 00:17:20,839
Who knows
how long God shall grant it to us?

199
00:17:50,880 --> 00:17:53,759
It's been a long time
since I've felt this good.

200
00:17:54,960 --> 00:17:56,839
Cheers!

201
00:17:58,880 --> 00:18:00,919
Come here, Fleurette!

202
00:18:10,760 --> 00:18:12,759
