and finish our dance.

207
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:06,039
The Huguenots are coming!
Retreat to your houses!

208
00:19:06,120 --> 00:19:07,559
The Huguenots!

209
00:19:07,640 --> 00:19:09,719
The Huguenots are coming!

210
00:19:09,800 --> 00:19:11,879
Make haste, hide!

211
00:19:25,240 --> 00:19:28,879
Come, get inside!

212
